com.viewlift.views.customviews

Class ViewCreator.CollectionGridItemViewCreator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.viewlift.views.customviews.ViewCreator.CollectionGridItemViewCreator
  • Enclosing class:
    ViewCreator

    public static class ViewCreator.CollectionGridItemViewCreator
extends java.lang.Object
    This class encapsulates the data necessary for a tray item to create all the required UI components. This may be used for tray adapters so that each individual item in a RecyclerView may be created by the ViewCreate.createComponentView() method.
